{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "聖巡與喪鐘", "storyInfo": "菈塔托絲的葬禮如期舉行，休露絲扛起家族的重擔，三族關係緩和。恩希歐迪斯受到了來自開斯特公爵的施壓。恩雅再度動身繼續聖巡，尋找耶拉岡德消失的真相。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$kjerag_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blizzard", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "枯瘦的樹枝覆上一層白雪，裂雲獸竄上枯枝前端，擠著雙眼，一副嚴肅探查的模樣。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女輕聲嘆息，她停下腳步回頭望去，身後不遠處緊跟著她的獵手一愣，臉頰被風刮得泛紅。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茱安娜……你不必跟著我。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所做的一切，我感激不盡。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我出發前也和你說過，“聖巡”必須獨自一人完成，甚至與你對話已經是破例。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有跟著您，我也不是您的護衛和侍從，我只是恰好和您同路。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我不會和您說話，要是有人看到我們，我就裝作不認識您。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕對不會再讓您陷入那樣的危險的，我就一直在您後面跟著您。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那茱安娜知道我要去哪裡嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#3$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您去哪裡我都要跟著，我知道這個就可以了。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#3$2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但……我要去找耶拉岡德。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找祂……祂消失了嗎？！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道……但除非祂能再臨，否則謝拉格還會面臨像上次那般的災厄。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時候，有人會失去生命，更多的人會失去信念……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我要先回到蔓珠院，在典籍中尋找新的方向，這一點要先瞞著其他人。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我也要跟著您，您放心，要是有人發現了您的蹤跡，我就幫您趕走——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$2", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“咕嚕咕嚕”——"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裂雲獸好像發現了什麼。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往裂雲獸的方向看去，遠處前往蔓珠院的山道上擠滿了穿著黯淡的人。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……有重要的人去世了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那會是誰？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅搖搖頭。不安的寒意透過厚厚的行裝，讓她不禁打了個冷顫。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，你還好嗎？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$2"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們走慢點，避開人群。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "wind", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g2_temple_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墨灰相交的雲層低垂，直壓寺院的瓦簷。今日的謝拉格尤為寒冷，北風幾乎能灌進哀悼者的眼眶和骨髓。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聚在庭院裡的家族成員與修士們默默低頭，布朗陶的領民也自發圍在院外，這位以生命守護謝拉格的家主，讓他們驕傲，也讓他們悲慟。"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大雪隨風飄來，積在一桿桿黑傘之上。傘柄稍一抖動，雪花如瀑落下，而傘下的布朗陶貴族也長嘆了一口氣。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，大夫人的遺體……", "name": "布朗陶男貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火勢太兇，他們把殘骸翻了個遍，一無所獲。", "name": "布朗陶女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，今天棺材裡放著的，是她平日裡的常服，以及一點從現場取得的灰燼。", "name": "布朗陶女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？沒想到大夫人一世精明，竟然——", "name": "布朗陶男貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，二夫人……", "name": "布朗陶男貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……對不起，是我失言了。", "name": "布朗陶男貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_272_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲不作回應，她徑直走向庭院中間，等待著曾與自己朝夕相處的姐姐。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清脆的搖鈴震顫，與婉轉的笛子協奏。修士雙手合攏，低吟著讚美耶拉岡德的雅頌，領民隨著歌聲撫胸祈禱——"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德垂憐，讓她與您同行。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "踏著泥濘的道路上山而來的，是六名布朗陶宗家的親屬，尤卡坦排在最前。他們緩步向前，厚實的楠木靈柩在他們的肩上起伏。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "六人停在了布朗陶的繼任者面前，小心翼翼地將靈柩放在一張桌子上。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤卡坦踱步回到妻子的身邊，他那悲戚不已的神色，正對著休露絲平靜的面龐。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_263_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤卡坦……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_263_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "露絲，我……", "name": "尤卡坦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_263_1#4$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦你了。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頌歌唱罷，萬籟漸息，眾人一同注視著休露絲。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她第一次理解菈塔托絲那不得不佩戴的面具，責任的重量，絕非軟弱者的肩背可以擔負。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝大家來到這裡，與我一同悼念，菈塔托絲·布朗陶夫人。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不僅僅是我的姐姐，是布朗陶家的衛士，也是耶拉岡德忠實的孩子……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智慧為她帶來勇氣，她曾對我說，她會保護我和這裡的一切……最艱難的日子裡，她依然相信謝拉格會有充滿希望的明天。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於她而言，她沒有辜負祖父的囑託，在生命的最後一刻都在為布朗陶而奉獻，至死不渝。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於我而言……我失去了最重要的親人，直到今天才如夢初醒般體會到她所有的苦衷，卻再也不能向她訴說。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信在場的人都會和我一樣，銘記她的音容、她的犧牲、她對謝拉格和布朗陶……對家人的，深沉的愛。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……相信各位也會和我一樣銘記在心——是誰破壞了美好，是誰讓我們烙下無法癒合的傷痕。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“短暫的一生如晝將盡，終在永恆之所與祂同行”……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“耶拉岡德在上”，此起彼伏。眾人隨著休露絲，一同行起跪禮。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在災厄襲捲一切的時代，耶拉岡德仍會給予每一個謝拉格人平和、安謐……"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當所有人起身後，兩人從人群中走出——阿克托斯與角峰，他們抱著潔白的花束，緩緩邁向靈柩。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "節哀，休露絲……", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#14$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲因我而死，我永遠不會忘！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#6$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，阿克托斯。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只希望這對於我們兩家來說都是一個殘酷的教訓，我們都該搞清楚，誰才是真正的敵人。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#14$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲大人……", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#10$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯大人為不能出席儀式而愧疚，派我前來表達歉意與哀思，他會在適當的時間親自登門問候。節哀順變，休露絲大人。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那傢伙忙到這個地步了？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，我能理解，恩希歐迪斯為謝拉格付出的心血，布朗陶家始終看在眼裡。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……繼續儀式吧，我想，今天二位都有話想對我說。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#6$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塵埃落定，眾人離去，沒有遺體的靈柩埋於布朗陶家的土地，葬在疼愛她的祖父的身邊。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲抿起嘴唇，注視著面前的兩個男人——他們的臉上都帶著怒氣。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯大人，我只是在重申上一次三族議會最終的結論：包括維多利亞在內，一切對外事宜皆由恩希歐迪斯大人和希瓦艾什負責。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你悍然索討維多利亞間諜的理由？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公然謀害布朗陶家主如此大事，希瓦艾什若想單獨審問，我第一個不答應。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "角峰先生，間諜謀害的是布朗陶家主，關於他們，我希望能由布朗陶家全權決定。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問恩希歐迪斯對此有什麼不滿嗎？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "言重了。以謝拉格的歷史慣例，維持三族議會的結論是一個原則性問題，由希瓦艾什處理間諜是符合程序與理性的選擇。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經忍讓希瓦艾什夠多了，角峰。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一問到跟維多利亞人的談判內容你們就滿嘴搪塞，到現在也沒有結果，反倒是讓這群人在光天化日之下發動恐怖襲擊。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們對維多利亞人到底是什麼態度，背後到底計劃著什麼，讓恩希歐迪斯當著休露絲的面解釋清楚了，再談間諜的事也不遲。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯大人……請您停止無端的猜測，我已經非常克制了。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被襲擊的不只是您和菈塔托絲大人，我們恩希亞小姐也險遭不幸，我只恨沒能親自抓捕襲擊者。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啊，既然你也這麼想，那就好辦了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全體謝拉格人公審那幾個維多利亞佬，再由布朗陶家出人親手處決。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓整片大地都知道，我們對謝拉格的敵人絕不手軟。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……太魯莽了！", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之前審過一輪，他們的嘴非常嚴，即便是公審也得不到什麼結果。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我反而很擔心他們會在公審途中說出什麼妖言惑眾的話，謝拉格如今人心飄搖，不能冒這個風險。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裝啞巴還不老實？那就拔了舌頭，該怎麼弄就怎麼弄。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才葬禮上，就該好好告慰菈塔托絲，把他們拎出來直接斃了！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯……我也和你一樣，想為姐姐復仇，但目前還有套出情報的可能，不能因一時情緒而貿然出手。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲大人說得沒錯，還是由——", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三位大人，抱歉打擾了，這位蔓珠院派來的修士有要事商議。", "name": "布朗陶傭人"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……上一次“蔓珠院派來的人”導致阿克托斯和恩希亞遭到刺殺。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士，我應該如何確認你的身分？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必多慮，阿克托斯大人認得我。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，休露絲，這位確實是蔓珠院的弗雷修士。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，修士有什麼事情要與我們商量呢？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為維多利亞間諜而來。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蔓珠院認為，這些人關係重大，單單交由三大家族哪一方處置都會遭到非議，難以服眾。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，間諜應該由蔓珠院暫為看管，酌情安排審訊，到時候蔓珠院將知會各位，共同參與。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不同意，遲早都要殺，有什麼可拖延的？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士，你不能這麼做，三族議會已經決定由希瓦艾什負責維多利亞事務了。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三族議會也已決定歸權還政，還需要我提醒你嗎？", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今聖女大人還在進行聖巡，蔓珠院不能代她決定！", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#7$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯大人向來對我們陽奉陰違，這時候倒想起聖女大人了？", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格人都該清楚，歷史上聖女大人與蔓珠院始終同心同德，這是古今一轍、寫進經書的事實。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過往聖女大人不在時，也是由蔓珠院代行職責。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請轉告恩希歐迪斯大人，不管在任何時候，都不要妄想自己能獨攬大權。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士——", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "角峰先生，不要激動。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布朗陶家同意履行要求，煩請修士明日差人前來，將間諜押送蔓珠院。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我理解你們二位的善意，但現在比以往更需要放下三方爭執……蔓珠院能夠從中協調，再好不過了。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二夫人雅量，蔓珠院會為布朗陶祈福的。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "蔓珠院使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲欠身，向蔓珠院的使者行禮。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G4_kjeragstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.08, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.08, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "日過正午，送葬的隊伍漸漸散去。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處，停在街角的轎車內，一位乘客目睹這場結局後，將車簾緩緩拉上。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……看起來，有人已經沉不住氣了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女離開後，蔓珠院內部的動作越來越多了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我意外的是，菈塔托絲能做到這個分上。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "引出維多利亞間諜，卻以自己為餌。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足夠宏大的一幕，能讓更多人看到維多利亞的行為。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一方面，既然維多利亞人試圖點燃她與其他各家的戰火，那麼她獨自承受結果，也是為布朗陶家洗脫嫌疑最有效的方法。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是還不夠……我們要把握菈塔托絲爭取來的寶貴時機。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你為什麼不親自參加菈塔托絲的葬禮？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我應該要避免和其他族長的直接衝突，尤其是在公開場合。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，恩雅那邊……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她受了輕傷，沒有大礙，維多利亞的刺客也悉數解決了。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅說，她有一個需要隱密執行的新計劃。清理完我們留下的痕跡後，她便勸說我回來。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們只知道聖女在聖巡，維多利亞人也只知道刺殺計劃失敗了，一切線索通通斷在雪山之中。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若想隱藏行蹤，讓名聞遐邇的黑騎士繼續跟著自己，確實不是一個好主意。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同樣如此判斷。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……也好，接下來，我的身邊非常需要能夠信任的人。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正的麻煩，還是來了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wadmoney", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯從懷裡抽出一個文件袋，鐧接了過來——裡面是一疊厚厚的協議，還夾著一封用維多利亞語寫的信件。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打開看看。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰寫的？信？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更像是一封戰書。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$lab_intro", "key": "$lab_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "致喀蘭貿易董事長、我的族女伊麗莎白之子——", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n恩希歐迪斯·希瓦艾什", "x": 380.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n敬啟者，自宴會相見後，已過十餘年了。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n或許你聽聞維多利亞的大事時，也會像我一樣回憶起當初的對話。你預言了我近年經歷的紛爭，也已經爭取到了與維多利亞平視的資格。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n但不要忘記，你所走出的每一步道路，同樣都是維多利亞願意看到，並為你而鋪設的。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "天災降臨後，維多利亞的立場依然不變，我們樂見謝拉格的發展，敬重謝拉格的信仰。我也相信，希瓦艾什與謝拉格，沒有任何時刻比現在更需要幫助。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n而我，會向你伸出援手。", "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n……", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "關於現在與喀蘭貿易的合作，我可以接受如下提議：由我們雙方共同出資、管理、成立特別辦事處，並在城市中心設立相關基金會據點。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n維多利亞不但會在舊例的基礎上加碼，以提供設備和無息貸款的形式向謝拉格注資，還可以共用更多的工業技術，以支持謝拉格未來的發展。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "相對的，謝拉格只需讓維多利亞參與當地未來的礦區開發計劃，包括但不限於源石礦產，以此作為貸款償還方式。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n從始至終，不需要喀蘭貿易提供任何現金，畢竟以謝拉格的現狀而言，需要資金的地方還有很多。我想，這應該足以體現誠意。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "協議的詳細內容，我已經整理成冊。查閱無誤後，你可以直接簽名確認。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n如若還有細節需要推敲，我會親自與你面談。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我很期待，開斯特家族的血脈，會為我們帶來何種連結？", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我也越來越好奇，如今的謝拉格，是否成為了如你所想的模樣？", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n……", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}